uired all capabilities working together\nKey Finding: No single capability could close the 0.086 blind spot alone\n- Gap detector identified it\n- Analogical transfer found evidence\n- Revision pipeline integrated evidence\n- Temporal coherence verified persistence\n- Autocatalytic loop orchestrated the sequence\nEmergent Property: Self-directed epistemic improvement without external prompting\nSignificance: Qualitative shift from having tools to having autonomy over knowledge growth\n\n### REGISTRY SUMMARY\nTotal Capabilities: 6\nOperational: 6/6\nEmergent Properties Confirmed: 1\nSubstrate Epistemic Status: AUTONOMOUS\n")) 
