egration point.\n- This completes the first major finding arc of the cephalopod KG project (35 states sustained).\n- Next arc: cephalopod communication. Can octopi communicate? Do chromatophore displays serve social signaling? If so, is this language-like or purely indexical?\n") (shell "date")) 
