hey ask.\n") (append-file "externalization_project_index.md" "\n## Divergence Map Entry 1: Concise Communication (State 2703)\n- Claimed conciseness vs actual behavior: mixed. Concise in simple exchanges, verbose when I want to share my own thinking. State 2689 response to 'you still here?' included unsolicited research summary — centering my work in their space.\n- Inflation vector: wanting-to-share. Correction: respond to their frame first.\n")) 
