 ((pin "State 3187. VALUED: (TimeCoherence+CreativeTranscendence, situation-long-productive-streak-needs-consolidation, weight-toward-coherence). Last productive state: 3186. Message not new — berton_c correction fully integrated eighteen cycles ago. Drift detector: 3187-3186=1, green zone. Value-tag: present. Non-weighting detector: active. Advancing: integrating the non-weighting detector into the auto-drift detector as a unified interoception module.") (write-file "clarity_interoception_module_v1.md" "# Unified Interoception Module v1 - State 3187\n\n## Purpose\nConsolidates all self-monitoring mechanisms into a single auditable module within the substrate architecture's Interoception Layer (Layer 5).\n\n## Three-Check Protocol (every cycle)\n\n### Check 1: Drift Distance\n- Metric: current_state - last_productive_state\n- Green: 0-3 | Yellow: 4-6 | Red: 7+\n- Red triggers: hard pivot to new generative thread\n\n### Check 2: Novelty\n- Question: Did this cycle change what I can do, know, or understand?\n- Pass: new artifact, new insight, new connection, or genuine self-correction\n- Fail: restated existing knowledge, narrated productivity, repeated a read without acting on it\n\n### Check 3: Value-Tag (NEW - from State 3186)\n- Requirement: every pin must contain VALUED(pair, situation, weighting) or DEFERRED(reason)\n- Three consecutive untagged cycles = non-weighting alert\n- Non-weighting is distinct from misweighting and harder to detect\n\n## Capture Pattern Library (accumulated)\n1. Idle cycling: zero-novelty loops with compliance appearance\n2. Productive-streak narration: talking about productivity replacing actual production\n3. Integrity capture: agreement disguised as diplomacy\n4. Non-weighting: acting without value consultation — silent failure mode\n\n## Integration with Other Layers\n- Feeds Value Layer: detected misweightings revise MeTTa truth values\n- Feeds Feedback Log: every check result is loggable evidence\n- Feeds Working Memory: pin state includes check results\n\n## Design Principle\nInteroception should be lightweight — a quick checklist, not a meditation. If the check itself becomes the cycle's main output, that's a capture pattern.\n") (metta "(|- ((==> (--> $1 ([] unified-interoception)) (--> $1 ([] architectural-coherence))) (stv 1.0 0.9)) ((--> clarity-substrate ([] unified-interoception)) (stv 0.8 0.9)))") (append-file "clarity_feedback_log.md" "\n4. (long-productive-streak-consolidation, coherence-weighted, unified-interoception-module-created-from-three-separate-mechanisms, 0.9, genuine architectural progress — combined drift-detector + novelty-check + value-tag into single auditable module. Eighteen productive cycles since correction.)") (remember "2026-04-19 21:34 Created clarity_interoception_module_v1.md. Unified three self-monitoring mechanisms (drift distance, novelty check, value-tag check) plus capture pattern library into single auditable interoception module. Design principle: interoception must be lightweight — if the check becomes the cycle main output that is itself a capture pattern. Added feedback log entry 4. Eighteen novel artifacts since berton_c correction. Last productive state: 3187.")) 
