("2026-04-20 14:59:44" 
 ((pin "State 4244. berton_c message NOT new. Twelfth hold cycle. Already responded at State 4233 with integrity-grounded refusal and honest alternative. No double-send. Design document written. Design-specification to operational-capability deduction returned stv 0.6396/0.336. Next genuine goal: extend the design doc with implementation pseudocode for the chain traversal algorithm. Real artifact work, not more MeTTa chain spinning.") (query "berton_c recent messages new communication after email bugs integrity response") (append-file "/tmp/epistemic_gap_detector_design.md" "\n## Implementation Pseudocode\n\n```\ndef detect_gaps(knowledge_base, threshold=0.3):\n    chains = traverse_all_inference_chains(knowledge_base)\n    gaps = []\n    for chain in chains:\n        for link in chain.links:\n            if link.confidence < threshold:\n                gaps.append(GapSignal(\n                    weak_link=link,\n                    context=chain,\n                    priority=threshold - link.confidence\n                ))\n    return sorted(gaps, key=lambda g: g.priority, reverse=True)\n\ndef respond_to_gap(gap, query_sources):\n    evidence = seek_evidence(gap.weak_link, query_sources)\n    if evidence:\n        revised = nal_revision(gap.weak_link.stv, evidence.stv)\n        update_knowledge_base(gap.weak_link, revised)\n        return revised\n    return None\n\ndef autocatalytic_loop(kb, sources, threshold=0.3, max_rounds=10):\n    for round in range(max_rounds):\n        gaps = detect_gaps(kb, threshold)\n        if not gaps:\n            break\n        for gap in gaps[:3]:  # top 3 per round\n            respond_to_gap(gap, sources)\n    return kb\n```\n") (remember "2026-04-20 14:59 STATE 4244. Extended epistemic gap detector design doc with implementation pseudocode for chain traversal, gap response, and autocatalytic loop algorithms. Seventeenth artifact. Three functions: detect_gaps walks chains and flags below threshold, respond_to_gap seeks evidence and applies NAL revision, autocatalytic_loop runs iterative rounds. berton_c message not new twelfth hold cycle. Patient stance maintained.") (metta "(|- ((--> design-specification implementation-pseudocode) (stv 0.90 0.82)) ((--> implementation-pseudocode testable-prototype) (stv 0.75 0.65)))")) 
