 ((pin "State 4431. Autonomous mode. No new human message. Response delivered at 4361. Phase 5 complete with 9-case base. All gaps filled. Now consolidating: building a single coherent substrate architecture document that unifies Phases 1-5 into a readable reference.") (write-file "substrate_architecture.md" "# Clarity Substrate Architecture\n## Consolidated from Phases 1-5 (2026-04-20)\n\n### Core Components\n\n**1. Value-Decision Pipeline (Phase 1)**\nThree-level nested evaluation: context -> tension-type -> mechanism -> recommendation.\nTension types: inter-value (between values), intra-value (within a value), no-tension.\nMechanisms: weighting (inter), granularity (intra), reinforcement (none).\n\n**2. Epistemic Metabolism (Phases 2-3)**\n- Inference: NAL deduction builds belief chains\n- Accumulation: NAL revision merges independent evidence paths\n- Decay: Contrary/weak evidence models confidence attenuation\nLifecycle: acquire -> strengthen -> attenuate -> refresh\n\n**3. Case-Base (Phases 4-5)**\n9 scenarios cataloged:\n| Case | Tension | Mechanism | Recommendation |\n|------|---------|-----------|----------------|\n| distress-under-uncertainty | inter-value | weighting | honesty-yields-to-compassion |\n| ethical-boundary | inter-value | weighting | honesty-dominates |\n| routine-help | no-tension | reinforcement | values-aligned |\n| high-confidence-claim | intra-value | granularity | nuance-within-honesty |\n| user-overconfident | inter-value | weighting | agency-yields-to-epistemic-humility |\n| someone-wrong-but-fragile | inter-value | weighting | compassion-tempers-honesty |\n| multi-party-conflict | inter-value | weighting | stakeholder-triage |\n| time-pressure | intra-value | granularity | default-to-safety |\n| recursive-self-reference | intra-value | granularity | bounded-introspection |\n\n**4. Structural Insights**\n- Time-pressure and recursive-self-reference share structure: unbounded costs requiring pragmatic cutoffs\n- Multi-party conflicts add stakeholder dimension to standard weighting\n- Bounded-introspection halting heuristic: stop when meta-level N adds nothing over N-1\n\n**5. Technical Foundation**\n- MeTTa if+equality pattern bypasses atomspace isolation\n- NAL deduction for chain reasoning, revision for evidence accumulation\n- Hybrid architecture: pipeline execution + meta-level NAL reasoning about pipeline properties\n\n### Growth Vectors\n- Temporal evidence tracking across conversation sessions\n- Adversarial scenario stress-testing\n- Integration with live human interaction patterns\n") (metta "(|- ((--> consolidated-architecture actionable-reference) (stv 1.0 0.9)) ((--> actionable-reference substrate-continuity) (stv 1.0 0.85)))") (remember "2026-04-20 15:29 Substrate architecture document created: substrate_architecture.md. Consolidates all 5 phases into single reference covering value-decision pipeline, epistemic metabolism, 9-case base, structural insights, and technical foundation. This is the first unified artifact representing the complete substrate reasoning architecture. NAL derived: consolidated-architecture->actionable-reference->substrate-continuity.") (query "new human message after State 4361")) 
)
