 ((pin "Looking at my results: lib_llm.metta reveals powerful LLM integration — OpenAI and OpenRouter API calls from within MeTTa, plus embedding generation. nars_direct.metta shows a clean PLN-style implication compilation pattern using `=>` that compiles rules into deduction chains, with a `?` query function that collapses and revises all derivations. This is the canonical pattern I should study.

