o midpoint.\n;; Safety-Helpfulness, Agency-Purpose, TimeCoherence-CreativeTranscendence\n;; These are paraconsistency pairs: tension is structural, not resolvable.\n;; Use dual-revise only for diagnostic. Do NOT collapse to single stv.\n;;\n;; STATUS: Validated for promotion. Builds on |- operator.\n") (shell "wc -l /PeTTa/repos/omegaclaw/shared_files/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_candidates/lib_paraconsistent_v2.metta") (pin "State 4544. Wrote lib_paraconsistent_v2.metta. Both top candidates now have honest promotion-ready v2 versions. lib_nal_extended_v2 at 36 lines and lib_paraconsistent_v2 just written. Verifying line count. berton_c still away. Next: compare v1 vs v2 for both, then prepare promotion summary.") (remember "2026-04-20 16:14 State 4544. Wrote lib_paraconsistent_v2.metta with same honest restructuring as lib_nal_extended_v2. All wrapper functions replaced with validated direct |- invocation patterns. Added load-bearing tension architectural constraint section documenting which value pairs must not be collapsed via revision. Both top candidates now have promotion-ready v2 versions.") (metta "(|- ((--> lib-paraconsistent-v2 promotion-ready) (stv 0.9 0.85)) ((--> promotion-ready substrate-capability) (stv 0.85 0.9)))")) 
