ss_agency_native.metta / compass_thinking_native.metta / compass_wonder_native.metta\n- compass_atoms.metta / compass_orchestrator.metta\n- response_compass_prototype.metta - evaluates responses against soul values\n- soul_kernel.metta / soul_values.metta / soul_governance_atoms.metta\n- soul_phase2_prototype.metta - lib_nal as soul inference engine\n- soul_targets_namespace.metta - predicate for mutation lock\n- soul_loop.metta - loop skeleton\n- gate_integration_wiring.metta - gate wiring\n\n### TIER 4: KNOWLEDGE BASE / ATOM SETS\n- berton_soul_kernel.metta (624 lines, largest file) - master kernel\n- substrate_kb.metta - 18 NAL atoms canonical definition\n- flourishing_source_atoms_v2.metta - NAL ==> with stv\n- paradox_fields.metta / paradox_mapping.metta / per_value_tensions.metta\n- self_model_atoms.metta / self_model_v1.metta\n- relational_memory.metta - 9-dim exchange memory field\n- tension_episodes.metta / tension_feedback.metta\n- emotion_integration.metta / vad_routing_substrate.metta\n\n### TIER 5: DRAFTS / PROTOTYPES\n- output_intercept_draft.metta / output_intercept_impl.metta\n- mutation_lock_upgrade.metta\n- person_state_staleness_fix.metta\n- mycelial_loop.metta - fungal network metaphor\n- epistemic_gap_detector.metta\n- counterfactual_method.metta\n- self_exercise.metta\n- precedent_memory.metta\n- layer1_precompute.metta\n- probe_test.metta\n\n### TIER 6: TEST / VALIDATION HARNESS\n- run_validation.metta - loads all soul_impl in order\n- integration_tests.metta\n- test_quantale.metta\n\n### KEY INTEGRATION POINT\nbackbone_update_policy.metta line 34: replace (meet ...) with (governance-pbit ...) to wire stv_pbit_adapter.metta into the live path.\n") (remember "READINESS_ASSESSMENT.md written 2026-04-20: 70 files classified into 6 tiers - Validated/Promotion-Ready, Functional Libraries, Compass/Soul Infrastructure, Knowledge Base/Atom Sets, Drafts/Prototypes, Test Harness. Key integration point remains backbone line 34 meet to governance-pbit wir