pe propagation: changing governance-score return type from stv to pbit affects all callers\n- Mitigation: pbit-to-stv exists in pbit_algebra if backward compat needed\n\n### Status: DRAFT — awaiting attractor basin line reads to finalize step 2\n") (append-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_candidates/clarity_feedback_log.md" "\n## Cycle 4709 - 2026-04-20 18:45\nWIRING_PLAN.md drafted. Covers backbone line 34, soul_attractor_basin call sites, import chain, verification steps, and downstream type propagation risk. Reading attractor basin meet call sites to finalize step 2. Assessment closed, now in active integration planning phase.\n") (pin "State 4709. Msg NOT new. WIRING_PLAN.md drafted with 5 concrete steps. Reading soul_attractor_basin lines 20-30 and 140-150 to finalize the exact meet call sites for step 2. Once attractor basin data is in, will finalize plan and begin actual code changes. Awaiting berton_c.")) 
