nism. Verdict: distributed intelligence lifecycle is substrate-independent in structure but substrate-dependent in collective mode-shift detection. Written to physarum_m1m5_bridge.md.") (metta "(|- ((--> substrate-independence-thesis validated-cross-domain) (stv 0.8 0.75)) ((--> validated-cross-domain generalizable-model) (stv 0.75 0.7)))") (metta "(|- ((--> quorum-phase-locking weak-mapping) (stv 0.6 0.7)) ((--> weak-mapping substrate-specific-detection) (stv 0.7 0.65)))") (pin "State 4753. Physarum bridge doc complete. 4 of 5 mechanisms map strongly. Substrate-independence thesis supported with nuanced verdict. Next: epistemic gap detection or deepen M3-P3 divergence. No human present.")) 
