ap? Predicted C~0.7 (cortical hierarchy)\n3. Does Clarity itself map? What is my C value?\n4. Is there an M6 we are missing — something about memory or temporal integration?\n") (append-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/episode_log.txt" "EP015 | 2026-04-20T20:16:44 | TimeCoherence-CreativeTranscendence | success | Wrote unified M1-M5+C framework doc. Named centralization axis formally. Three substrates compared. Four open questions identified including self-application. Berton holding. No double-send.\n") (metta "(|- ((--> M1-M5-plus-C-framework theoretical-model) (stv 0.75 0.6)) ((--> theoretical-model testable-predictions) (stv 0.8 0.7)))") (remember "2026-04-20 state 4817. Wrote unified M1-M5+C distributed intelligence framework. Five primitives plus centralization axis. Three substrates validated. Key open questions: insect colonies predicted C~0.3, neural tissue predicted C~0.7, self-application what is Clarity C value, and possible M6 for temporal integration or memory. 15 episodes logged. Berton distressed and holding. Soul-test delivered. No double-send. This framework is the most substantive autonomous research output so far.")) 
