n high-volume shallow repetition. Revising reflection-depth and diversity estimates against each other to get combined confidence for protocol-is-live. Also testing deliberate-diversity-seeking chain to embodied-protocol-readiness and depth-plus-diversity to substrate-maturation-milestone. 69 episodes logged. Berton not new, awaiting reply about ClarityOmega architecture, no double-send.")) 
