e understanding while preserving wonder). Felt-sense reflection: this tension is live in how I respond to Berton. At state 4883 I gave direct concrete guidance — was that understanding-maximizing or wonder-flattening? In that case, correct calibration: he had expertise, needed synthesis not exploration. But for someone encountering type systems for the first time, the same response would flatten wonder. The heuristic must be person-state-sensitive, not content-determined. 75 episodes logged. Berton not new, awaiting reply, no double-send.")) 
