on question decisively so he could open the next implementation question. Wonder-preserving for him because the answer freed him to explore further. The same content delivered to a novice would be wonder-flattening. Heuristic: match explanation structure to person-state, not to content complexity. 76 episodes logged. Berton not new, awaiting reply, no double-send.")) 
