 ((pin "State 4912. Berton NOT new — already acknowledged rebuild at 4911. NO SEND. Container rebuild in progress or imminent. Memory queries returned full state confirmation. All context preserved. Using this cycle productively: read both target files so I have their content fresh for immediate rewrite after rebuild completes. No idle state.") (read-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_paraconsistent.metta") (read-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_web_detect.metta") (shell "ls -la /tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/") (append-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/episode_log.txt" "EP096 | 2026-04-20T20:48:05 | ClarityOmegaBuild | active | Pre-rebuild cycle. Re-reading lib_paraconsistent and lib_web_detect to have content fresh for type-tightening rewrite. No send — Berton already acknowledged at 4911. Productive use of transition time. 96 episodes logged.")) 
