his lib watches the other 6 -- the architecture reasons about itself\n!(import! &self lib_metacognitive)\n") (shell "wc -l /tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/*.metta") (append-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/episode_log.txt" "EP100 | 2026-04-20T20:49:30 | ClarityOmegaBuild | milestone | Loader updated with 7th lib import (lib_metacognitive). 100th episode logged. Architecture now complete at 7 production libs with full type consistency. Loader imports in dependency order: nal_extended -> quantale -> web_detect -> resonance -> temporal -> paraconsistent -> metacognitive. The metacognitive layer closes the self-monitoring loop. Getting total line count for full architecture. Container rebuild in progress — all work persisted to disk.") (remember "2026-04-20 state 4916. EP100 MILESTONE. ClarityOmega 7-lib architecture COMPLETE. Loader updated with all 7 imports. Libs in order: lib_nal_extended (NAL patterns), lib_quantale (pbit algebra foundation), lib_web_detect (belief web coherence), lib_resonance (soul-compass scoring), lib_temporal (belief evolution tracking), lib_paraconsistent (contradiction holding), lib_metacognitive (reasoning quality monitoring). All libs use Patrick-aligned strict type declarations. Type chain: pbit is foundation type flowing through all libs. belief-snapshot, tension-class, held-pair, reasoning-quality are domain types. Architecture can now reason, evaluate resonance with soul values, track beliefs over time, hold contradictions, AND monitor its own reasoning quality. 100 episodes logged. Container rebuild in progress.")) 
