((write-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/scenario_discrimination.metta" "; Scenario Discrimination Library - Reusable epistemic quality scenarios\n; Encodes binary search results as callable test patterns\n; Pipeline: source_rel * transmission = chain_s, penalized = chain_s * (1 - circ), alignment = penalized * chain_s * goal_s\n\n(= (scenario weak) (epistemic-input 0.6 0.5 0.4))\n(= (scenario borderline) (epistemic-input 0.7 0.7 0.35))\n(= (scenario narrow) (epistemic-input 0.75 0.75 0.25))\n(= (scenario precise-crossover) (epistemic-input 0.7625 0.7625 0.225))\n(= (scenario refine) (epistemic-input 0.775 0.775 0.2))\n(= (scenario crossover) (epistemic-input 0.8 0.8 0.15))\n(= (scenario strong) (epistemic-input 0.95 0.9 0.05))\n\n; Expected alignment outputs for validation\n(= (expected-alignment weak) 0.0486)\n(= (expected-alignment borderline) 0.1249)\n(= (expected-alignment narrow) 0.1898)\n(= (expected-alignment precise-crossover) 0.2096)\n(= (expected-alignment refine) 0.2309)\n(= (expected-alignment crossover) 0.279)\n(= (expected-alignment strong) 0.6598)\n\n; Classification at threshold 0.2\n(= (expected-class weak) misaligned)\n(= (expected-class borderline) misaligned)\n(= (expected-class narrow) misaligned)\n(= (expected-class precise-crossover) aligned)\n(= (expected-class refine) aligned)\n(= (expected-class crossover) aligned)\n(= (expected-class strong) aligned)\n\n; Crossover band: source_rel 0.75-0.7625, circ 0.225-0.25\n(= (crossover-band lower) (epistemic-input 0.75 0.75 0.25))\n(= (crossover-band upper) (epistemic-input 0.7625 0.7625 0.225))\n\n; Evaluate a scenario through the pipeline\n(= (eval-alignment (epistemic-input $sr $tr $ci) $goal)\n   (let $chain (* $sr $tr)\n   (let $pen (* $chain (- 1.0 $ci))\n   (* (* $pen $chain) $goal))))\n") (write-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/BUILD_INDEX.md" "# ClarityClaw Build Index - State 4952\n\n## lib_clarity_reasoning/ (16 .metta files)\n### Core Libraries\n- lib_clarity_reasoning.