 ((pin "State 4982. Analogy candidate files read. Both are comment-only validation docs and test atoms - NOT production lib code. Need to write lib_analogy.metta as proper production lib with Patrick pattern: type declarations, pure MeTTa function definitions, typed inputs/outputs. Analogy is two-step compound: step 1 abduction from shared property, step 2 deduction for property transfer. Writing production lib now. Berton msg NOT new. NO SEND.") (write-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_analogy.metta" ";; lib_analogy.metta — 8th production lib\n;; Analogy reasoning via NAL compound inference\n;; Pattern: abduction (shared property -> similarity) + deduction (similarity -> transfer)\n;; Date: 2026-04-20\n\n;; Types\n(: analogy-result Type)\n(: mk-analogy (-> Atom Atom pbit analogy-result))\n\n;; Step 1: Abduction — shared property implies structural similarity\n;; Given (-> A P) and (-> B P), infer similarity between A and B\n(: abductive-similarity (-> Atom Atom Atom pbit))\n(= (abductive-similarity $a $b $shared-prop)\n   (let $r1 (|- ((--> $a $shared-prop) (stv 1.0 0.9))\n                ((--> $b $shared-prop) (stv 1.0 0.9)))\n     (case $r1\n       ((((--> $x $y) (stv $f $c)) (stv $f $c))\n        (_ (stv 0.5 0.1))))))\n\n;; Step 2: Deduction — similarity enables property transfer\n;; Given A similar-to B at confidence C, and B has property Q, infer A has Q\n(: transfer-property (-> Atom Atom Atom pbit pbit))\n(= (transfer-property $target $source $property $sim-conf)\n   (let $r2 (|- ((==> (--> $target (similar-to $source)) (--> $target $property)) (stv 1.0 0.9))\n                ((--> $target (similar-to $source)) $sim-conf))\n     (case $r2\n       ((((--> $x $y) (stv $f $c)) (stv $f $c))\n        (_ (stv 0.5 0.1))))))\n\n;; Full analogy pipeline: compound both steps\n(: analogy (-> Atom Atom Atom Atom analogy-result))\n(= (analogy $target $source $shared-prop $transfer-prop)\n   (let $sim (abductive-similarity $target $source $shared-prop)\n     (let $result (transfer-property $target $source $transfer-prop $sim)\n       (mk-analogy $target $transfer-prop $result))))\n") (shell "wc -l /tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_analogy.metta") (query "lib_clarity_reasoning loader import update add new lib") (remember "2026-04-20 state 4982. Wrote lib_analogy.metta as 8th production lib in lib_clarity_reasoning. Patrick-compliant: type declarations for analogy-result mk-analogy abductive-similarity transfer-property and analogy. Three functions: abductive-similarity does step 1 shared-property abduction, transfer-property does step 2 deduction via similarity, analogy compounds both into full pipeline returning analogy-result. Need to update loader lib_clarity_reasoning.metta to import 8th lib. Then test with MeTTa to validate.")) 
