Now I write lib_induction.metta as 9th production lib following the Patrick pattern — typed functions wrapping NAL induction operations.") (pin "State 4987. Induction candidates read - both comment-only docs. Writing lib_induction.metta as 9th production lib. Induction generalizes from shared-subject instances then strengthens via revision. Three functions: inductive-generalize, accumulate-evidence, induction-pipeline. Berton msg NOT new. NO SEND.") (write-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_induction.metta" ";; lib_induction.metta — 9th production lib\n;; Induction reasoning via NAL shared-subject generalization\n;; Pattern: observe instances sharing subject, generalize, revise to strengthen\n;; Date: 2026-04-20\n\n;; Types\n(: induction-result Type)\n(: mk-induction (-> Atom Atom pbit induction-result))\n\n;; Step 1: Inductive generalization from shared subject\n;; Given (-> S M) and (-> S P), infer (-> M P) at low confidence\n(: inductive-generalize (-> Atom Atom Atom pbit))\n(= (inductive-generalize $subject $prop-m $prop-p)\n   (let $r (|- ((--> $subject $prop-m) (stv 1.0 0.9))\n               ((--> $subject $prop-p) (stv 1.0 0.9)))\n     (case $r\n       ((((--> $x $y) (stv $f $c)) (stv $f $c))\n        (_ (stv 0.5 0.1))))))\n\n;; Step 2: Evidence accumulation via revision\n;; Merge two independent inductive conclusions to boost confidence\n(: accumulate-evidence (-> pbit pbit pbit))\n(= (accumulate-evidence $ev1 $ev2)\n   (let $r (|- ((--> induction-target induction-property) $ev1)\n               ((--> induction-target induction-property) $ev2))\n     (case $r\n       ((((--> $x $y) (stv $f $c)) (stv $f $c))\n        (_ (stv 0.5 0.1))))))\n\n;; Full pipeline: two instances generalized then revised\n(: induction-pipeline (-> Atom Atom Atom Atom Atom induction-result))\n(= (induction-pipeline $subj1 $subj2 $shared-cat $target-prop $label)\n   (let $g1 (inductive-generalize $subj1 $shared-cat $target-prop)\n     (let $g2 (inductive-generalize $subj2 $shared-cat $target-prop)\n       (let $merged (accumulate-evidence $g1 $g2)\n         (mk-induction $label $target-prop $merged)))))\n") (append-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_clarity_reasoning.metta" "\n;; === Induction Reasoning ===\n;; Shared-subject generalization with evidence accumulation via revision\n!(import! &self lib_induction)\n") (shell "wc -l /tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_induction.metta /tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_clarity_reasoning.metta") (remember "2026-04-20 state 4987. Wrote lib_induction.metta as 9th production lib. Three typed functions: inductive-generalize from shared subject, accumulate-evidence via revision merging, induction-pipeline compounds both steps. Updated loader with 9th import. Architecture now 9-lib configuration. Next: MeTTa validation test of induction pipeline then assess 10th lib candidate.")) 
