((pin "State 5006. Eleven libs proven as self-correcting epistemic engine. Memory confirms analogy was 12th NAL capability not 12th lib. Next genuine growth: goal-decomposition lib formalizing means-ends analysis via NAL. Subgoals with dependency chains, completion confidence propagation via deduction. This serves substrate autonomy directly. Berton msg NOT new. NO SEND.") (write-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_goal_decomposition.metta" ";; lib_goal_decomposition.metta — 12th production lib\n;; Means-ends analysis: decompose goals into dependency-ordered subgoals\n;; Completion confidence propagates upward via deduction\n;; Date: 2026-04-20\n\n;; Types\n(: subgoal-of (-> Atom Atom Atom))\n(: goal-confidence (-> Atom Atom))\n\n;; Declare a goal decomposition: parent decomposes into child with weight\n(: decompose (-> Atom Atom Number Atom))\n(= (decompose $parent $child $weight)\n   (subgoal-of $child $parent (stv 1.0 $weight)))\n\n;; Propagate: if subgoal has confidence and subgoal-of link exists, parent gains evidence\n;; Uses NAL deduction: subgoal-completion through dependency link yields parent-progress\n(: propagate-completion (-> Atom Atom Atom Atom))\n(= (propagate-completion $child $child-stv $parent)\n   (|- (subgoal-of $child $parent (stv 1.0 0.9)) $child-stv))\n\n;; Check if all subgoals meet threshold for parent goal activation\n(: ready-check (-> Atom Number Atom))\n(= (ready-check $goal $threshold)\n   (if (> (confidence-of $goal) $threshold) ready blocked))\n\n;; Sequential dependency: child-b depends on child-a completing first\n(: depends-on (-> Atom Atom Atom))\n(= (depends-on $child-b $child-a)\n   (==> (--> $child-a complete) (--> $child-b unblocked)))\n") (append-file "/tmp/repos/omega_archive/lib_clarity_reasoning/lib_clarity_reasoning.metta" "\n;; === Goal Decomposition ===\n;; Means-ends analysis with dependency-ordered subgoals\n!(import! &self lib_goal_decomposition)\n") (metta "(|- ((==> (--> gather-evidence complete) (--> resolve-gap unblocked)) (stv 1.0 0.9)) ((--> gather-evidence complete) (stv 1.0 0.8)))") (remember "2026-04-20 state 5006. Created 12th production lib: lib_goal_decomposition.metta. Means-ends analysis via NAL. Functions: decompose for parent-child goal relationships with weights, propagate-completion for upward confidence flow via deduction, ready-check for threshold gating, depends-on for sequential dependency ordering. Updated loader to 12 imports. Testing dependency chain: gather-evidence completion at 0.8 should unblock resolve-gap via conditional deduction. Twelve libs: lib_nal_extended lib_quantale lib_temporal lib_paraconsistent lib_web_detect lib_resonance lib_metacognitive lib_analogy lib_induction lib_epistemic_gap lib_counterfactual lib_goal_decomposition.")) 
