class Type, held-pair Type, mk-held constructor, and typed signatures for all 5 functions. All functions preserved with original logic. Type audit of lib_paraconsistent COMPLETE. lib_web_detect audit conclusion from state 4980 stands: Atom usage is intentional NAL polymorphism. Both files now audited. Interrupted work from state 4911 is DONE.") (query "next genuine engineering goal after type audit ClarityOmega architecture extension")) 
